column5: Good morning everyone,  Just a reminder for those who are thinking of coming out to the Markham swill, it's tonight at 6pm.  16th ave and Woodbine (in the corner of the No Frills plaza)  I'll be off to work in a short while but anyone having trouble finding the place can call me on my cell phone:  647-293-9874  Stan (HearingFish)
It s@*ks big time that I can't make it...I hope a few of you manage to get together and have a great time.  Maureen
